name: Huma Chia Energy Gel Raspberry
description: Smooth raspberry sweetness in an all-natural energy gels that are made from real fruit. Huma gels use no-nonsense all-natural ingredients that are easy to understand and easy to digest.Ingredients: Raspberry puree, evaporated cane juice, brown rice syrup, filtered water, ground chia seeds, sea salt, citric acid, natural caffeine.25mg of natural caffeine for an extra boost of energy.475mg of Omega-3 fatty acids per serving.
